=&quot;105&quot; class=&quot;xl980&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 245pt; height: 78.75pt;&quot;&gt;Obligatorio. Se debe informar Contrato o Tarjeta. Este dato es obligatorio si PAN no es informado. Si se informa se valida que contrato (Código de Entidad (CODENT) + Centro de Alta Cuenta (CENTALT) + Cuenta (CUENTA)) exista en tabla de contratos MPDT007&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr height=&quot;46&quot; style=&quot;height: 34.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;td height=&quot;46&quot; class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap; height: 34.5pt;&quot;&gt;02&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;CENTALT&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;CENTRO ALTA CUENTA&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl979&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Alfanumerico&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align