ack; white-space: nowrap; height: 15pt;&quot;&gt;05&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;OFIGEST&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;OFICINA GESTORA&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl979&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Alfanumerico&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Entrada&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;327&quot; class=&quot;xl980&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 245pt;&quot;&gt;Entrada se debe informar, y debe ser igual a la Oficina Gestora de la tabla MPDT007,&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr height=&quot;20&quot; style=&quot;height: 15pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;td height=&quot;20&quot; class=&quot;xl977&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap; height: 15pt;&quot;&gt;06&lt;/td&gt;&lt;